headline: Zimmer Biomet to Present at the 27th Annual Barclays Healthcare Conference
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH) today announced that members of the Zimmer Biomet management team will be presenting at the 27th Annual Barclays Healthcare Conference on Thursday, March 13, 2025, at 9:30 a.m. ET.
